# Valid scenario outline with examples
outline: Test multiple pet retrieval
  when I get a pet by ID
    call ^getPetById
      petId: {{petId}}
  then I see the expected name
    assert $.name equals {{expectedName}}
  examples:
    | petId | expectedName |
    | 1     | "Fluffy"     |
    | 2     | "Buddy"      |
    | 3     | "Charlie"    |
